1380x1ce7986760ade2bf0f322f5ef39ce0de3bd0c82bPonzICOwaterfall, kind ofyes/noSarcastic contract.This scheme gathers funds. Of each amount invested, half is kept by the owner. The other half is divided among previous investors in line. If they want, they can withdraw it. Some errors are present (running through a possible big array; if you invest twice, after a withdraw, you are added twice. The math used to split the invested money among the users seems wrong: it is not really proportional to what invested).
